verses.verse: Praise <S%H1984><s%> Yah! <S%H3050><s%> Praise <S%H1984><s%> God <S%H410><s%> in his sanctuary! <S%H6944><s%> Praise <S%H1984><s%> him in his heavens <S%H7549><s%> for his acts of power! <S%H5797><s%>
Praise <S%H1984><s%> him for his mighty acts! <S%H1369><s%> Praise <S%H1984><s%> him according to his excellent <S%H7230><s%> greatness! <S%H1433><s%>
Praise <S%H1984><s%> him with the sounding <S%H8629><s%> of the trumpet! <S%H7782><s%> Praise <S%H1984><s%> him with harp <S%H5035><s%> and lyre! <S%H5035><s%>
Praise <S%H1984><s%> him with tambourine <S%H8596><s%> and dancing! <S%H4234><s%> Praise <S%H1984><s%> him with stringed instruments <S%H4482><s%> and flute! <S%H5748><s%>
Praise <S%H1984><s%> him with loud <S%H8088><s%> cymbals! <S%H6767><s%> Praise <S%H1984><s%> him with resounding <S%H8643><s%> cymbals! <S%H6767><s%>
Let everything that has breath <S%H5397><s%> praise <S%H1984><s%> Yah! <S%H3050><s%> Praise <S%H1984><s%> Yah! <S%H3050><s%>
